Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}之后的{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}人生也毫无改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:12.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}总是把「无所谓」{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}挂在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:15.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}我的才能{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}尚未绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:20.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}既然不想赢{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}也不讨厌输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:26.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}冰冷如机械般的感情{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}为何会波动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:32.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}我们都是{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}暗藏潜力的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:38.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}却还要{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}永远蒙蔽自己的双眼活下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:44.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}心被压迫被掩盖 {\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}已经不再新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:49.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}即便如此还是{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}面色不改地活着的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:55.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}谁都蕴藏着 {\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}不自知的潜力
